title: Audiophile Reference I: Classical Music
description:
AUDIOPHILE REFERENCE 1- CLASSICAL MUSIC

[img]http://img151.imageshack.us/img151/9596/fim006.gif[/img]

Label:	First Impression Music
Genre:	Classical
Product No.:	CFIM 006

Format:	HDCD CD

A careful selection of classical pieces from the recordings of Golden String and First Impression Music to illustrate what reference an audiophile should use in gauging the quality of the sonic properties of an audio system or a recording. 13 of the best tracks of classical music from FIM recordings specially selected for gauging the performance of an audio system.
